project.description: Wavy is the go-to app for beachgoers seeking a secure and enjoyable shoreline experience. Designed for the coast, Wavy features an interactive map where users can view and place cautionary pins on potential hazards like rip tides, shark presence, or jagged rocks. Additionally, Wavy enhances your beach day by offering a local chat feature, allowing you to connect and share updates with fellow beachgoers in your area. Stay informed, stay safe, and make the most of your time at the beach with Wavy.
